content: Thank you for creating an awesome and fun app for the little ones! Keeps them entertained and teaches them many learning skills. I love the reactions I see from my nieces and nephews when they discover the interacting pieces. ☆☆☆☆☆
c Cute app for preschoolers to learn alphabet. Several levels of play: automatic movie, interactive or basic.
I bought this app for my daughter. It turns out to be her favorite. She loves learning her ABC with silly spin.
Silly Spin ABC has been helping my boy learn his ABC easily. He really enjoys using the App.
Best game for my child that ive found yet. Thank you for this!!!
This app is beautiful looking. I like the special features on each page. The 'fun facts' add to the joy of education while using this app. Congratulations on a well designed product.
